snippet.title: Making an IO game in a week! (swordbattle.io)
snippet.description:
PLAY SWORDBATTLE.IO: https://replit.com/@swordio/swordbattleio?v=1

Here is how I made sword.io...
My submission for KAJAM!

I made sword.io using Phaser, Socketio, and Nodejs. It's a 2d multiplayer sword fighting game! This is my submission for Replit's own game jam, Kajam! Hope you enjoy it.

Github: https://github.com/codergautam/swordbattle.io

Subscribe for more content like this (IT'S FREE)
Also join my Discord! https://bit.ly/CoderGautamDiscordServer
